ll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「I won a lucky draw and got a ticket for a Hot Spring trip!」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「Sorry again for the short notice, but can you come over and look after Hazuki again?」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The countryside I last visited in summer must have changed now that it's winter...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I wonder how she's been doing......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your thoughts wander as you pull yourself out of the heating table and get yourself ready for a trip to the contryside.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☆Character Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289580/extras/e34988ee2b6ffda4d8254a2f2b2399de.avif?t=1762324109\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3289580/extras_big/e34988ee2b6ffda4d8254a2f2b2399de.avif?t=1762324109 width=800 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Natsuhara Hazuki</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cousin and childhood friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's been a while since you met her last summer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She may not look so approachable, but that's only because</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >she's still exploring your relationship with you and her.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She doesn't swim in winter, so her tanlines are gone, and her hair grew longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She's no longer reluctant in bodily contact, and couldn't forget the days with you back in summer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>☆H Scenes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enjoy 3 kinds of H scenes throught out the game: HCG, H animation and pixel H animation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img